channel.title: TrimmedScape 317 release
channel.description:
PLEASE POST TO SORT OF KEEP THIS THREAD ALIVE SO PEOPLE NOTICE IT. IF NOT ITS FINE.
ATM IF YOU SEE THIS ANYWHERE ELSE ITS PROBABLY LEECHED, I'LL PROBABLY PUT IT SOMEWHERE ELSE, I am 'Archie15, or 'Finn' on the other main websites.
Hey guys, many of you probably don't know me as I often do not post on forums, or release much of my work, if its even worth releasing :|.
This is my old 317, I turned it off around May, and moved onto 508s. Back when I coded 317s Deltascape 'unfortunately' was the hot server, and as a new coder I picked it. It was not exactly the best choice, as it is a very messy source, although I believe it is the newer release someone had, it is not the extremely old one. But none-the-less this server was very fun to host, and I kept it up for well over 8 months, and still have TrimmedScape running.
I am not going to re-login and post pictures of it, but I have many video's of it on Youtube, check them out.
[b]**SUGGESTED YOU WATCH THE SUMMARY VIDEO**[/b] http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4XWxQ843Y0s&feature=channel_page -A summary video
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ipg41ZqZzdk&feature=channel - KBD (This spot is moved, a lot of it is in Yanille.)
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=04x0E4ccO2Y&feature=channel - A PK video of me VS a Player 'Cruz PK'
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IaxQSAFzmHM&feature=channel - A very old party I had back when the server started
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nrr1tki56GQ a player 'F U R Y' Pk video.
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ep-813nXq58&feature=related a player "Pure Ph33r" Pk Video
Pictures, sorry there not features just going threw 'My Pictures' to find some ;D
[IMG]http://i28.tinypic.com/t9gx7q.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i28.tinypic.com/kbvrcx.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i29.tinypic.com/n3rs6x.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i32.tinypic.com/2uiyk51.png[/img]
OTHER FEATURES THAT I SORT OF REMEMBER I ADDED,
-Added in a decent donator system, portal that you cannot enter without donators, never completed it - Some PKing fixes, not many. - A dialogue on object system (Was what I used to get from place to place) -Decent economy
Anyways, I cannot provide a client because I custom edited my client to load the cache from my website, I am sure any Delta client will work fine, along with bluurs if you put the edits in that are required with bluurs.
[code]EDIT TO THOSE WHO TRY TO USE BLUURRS CLIENT, IF IT GIVES YOU ERROR REFRESHING PACKET TYPE OF STUFF READ THIS --> http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,367375.0.html[/code]
Credits, I hate them, I don't care for them so here it is.
100% to anyone who wants it.
I am done with 317, was fun, but I have been on 508s for 5-6 months now, and really enjoy them.
-SERVER DOWNLOAD LINKS- http://uppit.com/v/5R7MW13B http://www.mediafire.com/?gzizhc5tdzn http://www.megaupload.com/?d=VELWTSCL
Knock yourself out,
Archer owner of TrimmedScape 508.
